<div class="container">
    <% first_name = @user.first_name.titlecase %>
    <h1>Welcome to breadshelf<%= first_name.present? ? ", #{first_name}" : '' %></h1>
    <%= image_tag(attachments['crumbs.png'].url, class: 'icon') %>
    <p>We're happy you've joined us!</p>
    <p>
        breadshelf is devoted to solving digital addiction through reading.
        You can learn more about us <a href="<%= @about_url %>">here</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
        The breadshelf product is coming soon. We'll notify you when it's ready.
        Do you have questions or feedback? Reply to this email!
    </p>
    <%= image_tag(attachments['slice.png'].url, class: 'icon') %>
    <p>We'd prefer you quit social media, but if you're on them follow us!</p>
    <div class="socials">
        <a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/readonbreadshelf">Instagram</a>
        <a class="link" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@readonbreadshelf">Tik Tok</a>
        <a class="link" href="https://x.com/readbreadshelf">X/Twitter</a>
    </div>
    <p>If you don't want to hear from us again, you can <a href="<%= @settings_url %>">unsubscribe</a>.</p>
    <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> breadshelf</p>
</div>